1
00:00:02,799 --> 00:00:06,000
<i>It's Matteo. </i>
<i>I came for you!</i>

2
00:00:07,719 --> 00:00:09,519
I'm sorry, Matteo.

3
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:14,759
<i>Our souls must suffer</i>

4
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:19,519
<i>and do good works</i>

5
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:25,800
<i>that break us of attachments</i>

6
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:29,519
<i>of sin and self.</i>

7
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,719
<i>Wake up!</i>

8
00:00:33,399 --> 00:00:34,840
<i>This...</i>

9
00:00:34,840 --> 00:00:36,799
<i>... is the word of God.</i>

10
00:00:48,039 --> 00:00:49,240
Matteo!

11
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:53,280
My brave boy.

12
00:00:57,119 --> 00:00:58,880
<i>What's happening?</i>

13
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:02,520
<i>I found you...</i>

14
00:01:04,719 --> 00:01:08,719
<i>... hanging in the barn.</i>

15
00:01:18,159 --> 00:01:22,159
<i>In this moment,</i>

16
00:01:22,159 --> 00:01:25,640
<i>you are on a middle plane.</i>

17
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,640
<i>Purgatory?</i>

18
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:52,640
<i>A place which offers salvation </i>
<i>and purification...</i>

19
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:57,359
<i>... in the form of a test.</i>

20
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:09,759
<i>It is a test you </i>
<i>have passed.</i>

21
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,759
Yeah, come this way!

22
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:13,520
<i>Thanks to your actions here,</i>

23
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:17,159
<i>you have purged </i>
<i>your venial sin of</i>

24
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:18,439
[gunshot]

25
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,280
<i>Cowardice.</i>

26
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,639
<i>You shall now...</i>

27
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:25,159
<i>... ascend.</i>

28
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:30,159
<i>... and Zanna?</i>

29
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:36,680
<i>She too has been tested.</i>

30
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:40,599
<i>To purge her soul</i>

31
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,520
[gasping]

32
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:49,560
<i>of her venial sin...</i>

33
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:53,000
<i>Selfishness.</i>

34
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,199
[gasping]

35
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,080
[crowd cheering]

36
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,360
<i>... and?</i>

37
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:12,400
<i>Has she done </i>
<i>enough to be saved?</i>

38
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,759
<i>No, my treasure...</i>

39
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:20,039
<i>She failed the ultimate test.</i>

40
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,159
<i>No, no, no...</i>

41
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:25,159
<i>She's a good person.</i>

42
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:27,240
Ah, yes?

43
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,639
Then why...

44
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:33,039
... did she abandon you?

45
00:03:45,199 --> 00:03:46,199
Cliff?

46
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:50,719
Cliff!

47
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:54,280
No, no, no, Cliff.

48
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,360
Cliff, wake up.

49
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:59,439
No, no, Cliff. 
Come on. Wake up.

50
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:01,719
My beautiful baby brother.

51
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,479
Cliff, you were right.

52
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:10,240
Life is to be lived.

53
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:15,319
<i>You have principles </i>
<i>but not rules.</i>

54
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:19,680
<i>... and you don't hold back,
but you're never out of control.</i>

55
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,759
[ambulance siren]

56
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:22,360
<i>... and you're kind.</i>

57
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,759
<i>You're so, so kind.</i>

58
00:04:25,199 --> 00:04:26,519
Wake up!

59
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,560
Cliff...

60
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:32,160
I am going to give you one 
last motivational speech, ok?

61
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,959
You listen to me.

62
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:36,879
Keep fucking fighting.

63
00:04:37,519 --> 00:04:39,720
Keep fighting because 
you deserve more time

64
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,639
to spread your amazing energy.

65
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:44,600
So, keep going. 
Keep fighting. Please!

66
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:47,120
[tearful]
Wake up, I love you.

67
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,120
Please...

68
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,680
Please.

69
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,639
I love you.

70
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:54,279
Wake up!

71
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,120
[crying]

72
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,360
Cliff?

73
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,720
No, no, no...

74
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,680
Cliff?!

75
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:12,079
What have you 
fucking done?!

76
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:14,120
What have you 
done with him?!

77
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,519
Please...

78
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:26,319
Give him back...

79
